'''麦克金利·摩根菲尔德'''（{{lang-en|McKinley Morganfield}}，{{bd|1913年|4月4日|1983年|4月30日}}<ref>Gordon pp. 4–5</ref>），艺名'''马迪·沃特斯'''（{{lang|en|'''Muddy Waters'''}}），是一位美国[[藍調|藍調]]音乐人，被称作“现代{{link-en|芝加哥藍調|Chicago blues}}之父”<ref name="cantbe-dvd">{{cite video |title=Muddy Waters — Can't Be Satisfied |format=DVD, 2003 |publisher=Winstar }}</ref>。Muddy Waters的影響力是巨大的，不僅僅是[[藍調|藍調]]和[[節奏藍調|節奏藍調]]，還有[[搖滾樂|搖滾樂]]，[[硬搖滾|硬搖滾]]，[[美國民間音樂|民間音樂]]，[[爵士樂|爵士樂]]和[[鄉村音樂|鄉村音樂]]。他經常使用[[放大器|放大器]]作為[[三角洲藍調|三角洲藍調]]和[[搖滾樂|搖滾樂]]之間形成的聯繫。<ref name="A Century of Champagne & Reefer">{{cite web|title=A Century of Champagne & Reefer|url=http://www.joyfulnoiserecordings.com/journal/muddy-waters/|publisher=Joyfulnoiserecordings.com|accessdate=30 April 2013|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130503013620/http://www.joyfulnoiserecordings.com/journal/muddy-waters/|archivedate=2013-05-03}}</ref><ref name="joyfulnoiserecordings.com">[http://www.joyfulnoiserecordings.com/journal/muddy-waters/ ''[[Rolling_Stone|Rolling Stone]]'', November 9, 1968.] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130503013620/http://www.joyfulnoiserecordings.com/journal/muddy-waters/ |date=五月 3, 2013 }} Quoted in "A Century of Champagne & Reefer". Retrieved 30 April 2013.</ref>。1987年入選[[搖滾名人堂|搖滾名人堂]]，2011年[[滾石雜誌一百大吉他手|滾石雜誌一百大吉他手]]評選為第49名<ref>[http://www.rollingstone.com/music/lists/100-greatest-guitarists-20111123/johnny-marr-20111122 滾石雜誌：最偉大的一百名吉他手]</ref>。

Muddy Waters在密西西比州[[克拉克縣_(密西西比州)|克拉克縣]]附近的斯托瓦爾種植園長大，17歲時他就彈奏吉他和口琴，模仿當地藍調藝術家Son House和[[羅伯·強生|羅伯·強生]]。<ref name="Guralnick">"His thick heavy voice, the dark colouration of his tone, and his firm, almost solid, personality were all clearly derived from House," wrote the music historian [[Peter_Guralnick|Peter Guralnick]] in ''Feel Like Going Home'', "but the embellishments, which he added, the imaginative [[slide_guitar|slide technique]] and more agile rhythms, were closer to Johnson."</ref>1941年，他被記錄在[[美國國會圖書館|美國國會圖書館]]的密西西比州藝術家上，由當時的圖書館主任[[阿蘭·洛馬克斯|阿蘭·洛馬克斯]]。<ref name="Palmer">
